Package lgp.lib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseInstruction<T>
    A built-in offering of the Instruction type.
    BaseInstructionGenerator<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Built-in offering of the InstructionGenerator interface.
    BaseProblem
    A basic skeleton for a problem setup with commonly used components and modules.
    BaseProblemParameters
    Parameters that can be given to configure a BaseProblem.
    BaseProblemTestResult
    Encapsulates the information given from a call to BaseProblem.test.
    BaseProgram<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    A built-in offering of the Program interface.
    BaseProgramGenerator<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    A ProgramGenerator implementation that provides effective BaseProgram instances.
    BaseProgramOutputResolvers
    A collection of built-in functions that can be used to resolve the output of a class BaseProgram instance.
    BaseProgramSimplifier<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Utility class that can be used to create a simplified representation of a BaseProgram.
    BaseProgramTranslator<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    A class ProgramTranslator implementation that converts class BaseProgram instances to a C-based representation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BaseProblemException
    Exception given when there is some problem with the setup of a BaseProblem.
